Sample Answer-1:
My greatest strength is my strong analytical and problem-solving skills. During my academic projects, I consistently demonstrated my ability to break down complex problems and find effective solutions. For instance, in one of the projects, I successfully identified a critical bug in the code and implemented a fix that improved the overall performance. About my weakness, I am working on improving my time management skills to ensure efficient task prioritisation and meet deadlines effectively.
Sample Answer-2:
One of my greatest strengths is my dedication to continuous learning and improvement. I actively seek opportunities to expand my knowledge and enhance my skills in the IT field. As for my weakness, I recognise the need to improve my presentation and communication skills, and I am committed to working on them to become a more effective communicator.
